{"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"DebugControllerDBusProtocol","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"DebugControllerDBusProtocol","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Protocol","title":"DebugControllerDBusProtocol","externalID":"s:3GIO27DebugControllerDBusProtocolP","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"protocol"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"DebugControllerDBusProtocol","kind":"identifier"},{"text":" : ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DebugControllerProtocol","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"DebugControllerProtocol","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO23DebugControllerProtocolP"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject0B8ProtocolP","text":"ObjectProtocol"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","type":"heading","anchor":"overview","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"It is a [iface","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Initable"},{"text":"] object, and will register an object at","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\/org\/gtk\/Debugging"},{"type":"text","text":" on the bus given as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[property"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DebugControllerDBus"},{"text":"] once it’s initialized. The","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"object will be unregistered when the last reference to the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDebugControllerDBus"},{"type":"text","text":" is dropped."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This D-Bus object can be used by remote processes to enable or disable debug","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"output in this process. Remote processes calling","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"org.gtk.Debugging.SetDebugEnabled()"},{"type":"text","text":" will affect the value of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[property"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DebugController"},{"type":"text","text":"] and, by default,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[func"},{"code":"GLib.log_get_debug_enabled","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, no processes are allowed to call "},{"code":"SetDebugEnabled()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" unless a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[signal[DebugControllerDBus](\/\/documentation\/gio\/debugcontrollerdbus\/onauthorize(flags:handler:)] signal handler is installed. This"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"is because the process may be privileged, or might expose sensitive","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information in its debug output. You may want to restrict the ability to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"enable debug output to privileged users or processes."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"One option is to install a D-Bus security policy which restricts access to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SetDebugEnabled()"},{"text":", installing something like the following in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"$datadir\/dbus-1\/system.d\/","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":":"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["<?xml version=\"1.0\"?> <!--*-nxml-*-->","<!DOCTYPE busconfig PUBLIC \"-\/\/freedesktop\/\/DTD D-BUS Bus Configuration 1.0\/\/EN\"","     \"http:\/\/www.freedesktop.org\/standards\/dbus\/1.0\/busconfig.dtd\">","<busconfig>","  <policy user=\"root\">","    <allow send_destination=\"com.example.MyService\" send_interface=\"org.gtk.Debugging\"\/>","  <\/policy>","  <policy context=\"default\">","    <deny send_destination=\"com.example.MyService\" send_interface=\"org.gtk.Debugging\"\/>","  <\/policy>","<\/busconfig>"],"syntax":"xml","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This will prevent the "},{"code":"SetDebugEnabled()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" method from being called by all"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"except root. It will not prevent the ","type":"text"},{"code":"DebugEnabled","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property from being read,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as it’s accessed through the "},{"code":"org.freedesktop.DBus.Properties","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" interface."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Another option is to use polkit to allow or deny requests on a case-by-case","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"basis, allowing for the possibility of dynamic authorisation. To do this,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"connect to the [signal[DebugControllerDBus](\/\/documentation\/gio\/debugcontrollerdbus\/onauthorize(flags:handler:)] signal and query"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"polkit in it:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"c","code":["  `g_autoptr(GError)` child_error = NULL;","  `g_autoptr(GDBusConnection)` connection = g_bus_get_sync (G_BUS_TYPE_SYSTEM, NULL, NULL);","  gulong debug_controller_authorize_id = 0;","","  \/\/ Set up the debug controller.","  debug_controller = G_DEBUG_CONTROLLER (g_debug_controller_dbus_new (priv->connection, NULL, &child_error));","  if (debug_controller == NULL)","    {","      g_error (\"Could not register debug controller on bus: `s`\",","               child_error->message);","    }","","  debug_controller_authorize_id = g_signal_connect (debug_controller,","                                                    \"authorize\",","                                                    G_CALLBACK (debug_controller_authorize_cb),","                                                    self);","","  static gboolean","  debug_controller_authorize_cb (GDebugControllerDBus  *debug_controller,","                                 GDBusMethodInvocation *invocation,","                                 gpointer               user_data)","  {","    `g_autoptr(PolkitAuthority)` authority = NULL;","    `g_autoptr(PolkitSubject)` subject = NULL;","    `g_autoptr(PolkitAuthorizationResult)` auth_result = NULL;","    `g_autoptr(GError)` local_error = NULL;","    GDBusMessage *message;","    GDBusMessageFlags message_flags;","    PolkitCheckAuthorizationFlags flags = POLKIT_CHECK_AUTHORIZATION_FLAGS_NONE;","","    message = g_dbus_method_invocation_get_message (invocation);","    message_flags = g_dbus_message_get_flags (message);","","    authority = polkit_authority_get_sync (NULL, &local_error);","    if (authority == NULL)","      {","        g_warning (\"Failed to get polkit authority: `s`\", local_error->message);","        return FALSE;","      }","","    if (message_flags & G_DBUS_MESSAGE_FLAGS_ALLOW_INTERACTIVE_AUTHORIZATION)","      flags |= POLKIT_CHECK_AUTHORIZATION_FLAGS_ALLOW_USER_INTERACTION;","","    subject = polkit_system_bus_name_new (g_dbus_method_invocation_get_sender (invocation));","","    auth_result = polkit_authority_check_authorization_sync (authority,","                                                             subject,","                                                             \"com.example.MyService.set-debug-enabled\",","                                                             NULL,","                                                             flags,","                                                             NULL,","                                                             &local_error);","    if (auth_result == NULL)","      {","        g_warning (\"Failed to get check polkit authorization: `s`\", local_error->message);","        return FALSE;","      }","","    return polkit_authorization_result_get_is_authorized (auth_result);","  }"]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DebugControllerDBusProtocol","type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol exposes the methods and properties of an underlying ","type":"text"},{"code":"GDebugControllerDBus","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" instance."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The default implementation of these can be found in the protocol extension below.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"For a concrete class that implements these methods and properties, see ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DebugControllerDBus"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Alternatively, use ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DebugControllerDBusRef","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" as a lighweight, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"unowned"},{"text":" reference if you already have an instance you just want to use.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"abstract":[{"code":"GDebugControllerDBus","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is an implementation of [iface","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DebugController"},{"type":"text","text":"]"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"which exposes debug settings as a D-Bus object.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DebugControllerDBusProtocol","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/debugcontrollerdbusprotocol"],"traits":[{"interf